snippet.textDisplay:
I love this bag so much! The fruit themed butterflies are cool - I do love that concept. And this is totally the sort of bag I'd go out with because I'm not one for boring bags and really love something more fun and unique. So this is actually something that if I saw it in a shop I'd want to buy it. But I'd probably also be a bit against it being a clutch as they are tricky to carry (plus anything that goes in my hands could get put down at any point and totally forgotten about, R.I.P in peace several umbrellas) and it also wouldn't fit my wallet and is too narrow for my phone (an old Nokia 3220). So I'd totally buy this and then not be able to figure out when to use it. Like I rarely carry money since I don't have any (ok so how did I buy the bag? I don't know, it just happened ok) and so it would just be my debit card in it and that's kinda odd - I'd just put it in a pocket instead. Hmmmm....
